OL,3,C'Yes, Pie Minister': Government urged
OL,4,Cto give pie and mash protected status
OL,6,FA former minister has urged the
OL,7,FGovernment to say "Yes, Pie Minister"
OL,8,Fand give traditional pie and mash
OL,9,Fprotected status to celebrate its
OL,10,Fcockney origins.
OL,12,FRichard Holden asked the Department
OL,13,Ffor Environment, Food and Rural
OL,14,FAffairs (Defra) to award Traditional
OL,15,FSpeciality Guaranteed (TSG) status for
OL,16,Fthe dish.
