OL,3,C'Yes, Pie Minister': Government urged
OL,4,Cto give pie and mash protected status
OL,6,FMr Holden said that if the meal,
OL,7,Fcomprising of a meat pie, mash
OL,8,Fpotatoes and a parsley sauce known as
OL,9,Fliquor, was in Italy or France it
OL,10,Fwould already be recognised.
OL,12,FLeading a Westminster Hall debate on
OL,13,FTuesday, the Conservative MP for
OL,14,FBasildon and Billericay said: "It is a
OL,15,Fstaple of cockney cuisine moving out
OL,16,Fto places like the east of England and
OL,17,Finto Kent as the cockney diaspora
OL,18,Fmoved post-war.
