OL,3,C'Yes, Pie Minister': Government urged
OL,4,Cto give pie and mash protected status
OL,6,F"That's the reason I have pie and mash
OL,7,Fshops in Basildon today, and we are
OL,8,Fseeking recognition to safeguard the
OL,9,Fheritage and to promote it both here
OL,10,Fand internationally."
OL,12,FHe added: "The pie, mash and liquors
OL,13,Fare freshly made to authentic family-
OL,14,Fown recipes passed down through
OL,15,Fgenerations like precious heirlooms.
OL,17,F"Something that, let's say in Italy or
OL,18,FFrance, would be instantly recognised
OL,19,Fas something worth celebrating and
OL,20,Fpreserving."
