OL,3,C'Yes, Pie Minister': Government urged
OL,4,Cto give pie and mash protected status
OL,6,FThe former Conservative Party chairman
OL,7,Fsaid France has 800 foods that have
OL,8,Fprotected status, with Italy having a
OL,9,Fsimilar figure and the UK lagging far
OL,10,Fbehind with fewer than 100.
OL,12,FThe TSG status is awarded to food
OL,13,Fproducts that have a particular
OL,14,Fproduction method and composition.
OL,16,FOther protection is afforded to
OL,17,Fproducts linked to specific areas,
OL,18,Fknown as Geographical Indication (GI)
OL,19,Fstatus.
