OL,3,C'Yes, Pie Minister': Government urged
OL,4,Cto give pie and mash protected status
OL,6,FBramley apple pies and Cornish pasties
OL,7,Fare foods that already have TSG status.
OL,9,FMr Holden referenced two pie and mash
OL,10,Fshops in his constituency, Robins Pie
OL,11,Fand Mash and Stacey's Pie and Mash,
OL,12,Fwhich act as "hubs of the community".
OL,14,FThe 39-year-old said he first tried
OL,15,Fthe meal after moving to London when
OL,16,Fhe was 19.
