OL,3,C'Yes, Pie Minister': Government urged
OL,4,Cto give pie and mash protected status
OL,6,FHe had told the PA news agency:
OL,7,F"Personally I prefer mine also with
OL,8,Fvinegar, some people have chilli
OL,9,Fvinegar ` it's not for me. It's not
OL,10,Fmalted vinegar, it's a specific sort
OL,11,Fof vinegar that they have with it."
OL,13,FDefra said an application for TSG
OL,14,Fstatus requires agreement on the
OL,15,Frecipe that producers would need to
OL,16,Ffollow to use the name in future and
OL,17,Fthey will assess the case once a
OL,18,Fformal application is submitted.
