OL,3,C'Yes, Pie Minister': Government urged
OL,4,Cto give pie and mash protected status
OL,6,FMr Holden's fellow Essex MP Mark
OL,7,FFrancois (Con, Rayleigh and Wickford)
OL,8,Fsaid the food was "cosmopolitan" owing
OL,9,Fto the variety in outlets that serve
OL,10,Fit.
OL,12,F"I now have two good (shops) in my
OL,13,Fconstituency, at Rayleigh Lanes Cafe
OL,14,Fand the Turkish cafe on the High
OL,15,FStreet, both of which do very good pie
OL,16,Fand mash, and that shows what a
OL,17,Fcosmopolitan food it's become."
