OL,3,C'Yes, Pie Minister': Government urged
OL,4,Cto give pie and mash protected status
OL,6,FMr Francois added: "I want to do
OL,7,Feverything I can to endorse his
OL,8,Fcampaign, to give it the recognition
OL,9,Fit really deserves."
OL,11,FHe later joked that he and Mr Holden
OL,12,Fmight have a contest to find the best
OL,13,Fpie and mash shop across their
OL,14,Fconstituencies.
OL,16,F"I'll pitch my pie and mash shops
OL,17,Fagainst him and we'll see, perhaps for
OL,18,Fcharity, who the winner will be," he
OL,19,Fsaid.
