OL,3,C'Yes, Pie Minister': Government urged
OL,4,Cto give pie and mash protected status
OL,6,FMr Holden said: "Just to really say to
OL,7,Feveryone, get out there, try that pie
OL,8,Fand mash, and to the minister, I hope
OL,9,Fthat we will be able to get this
OL,10,Fstatus and we will be able to say to
OL,11,Fyou 'Yes, Pie Minister'."
OL,13,FResponding for the Government,
OL,14,Fenvironment minister Daniel Zeichner
OL,15,Fsaid: "I can guarantee him this
OL,16,FGovernment's going to go big on food
OL,17,Fand regional food in general."
