OL,3,C'Yes, Pie Minister': Government urged
OL,4,Cto give pie and mash protected status
OL,6,FHe went on to say: "As a hearty meal
OL,7,Fwith roots in the docks of London, pie
OL,8,Fand mash has long been cherished as a
OL,9,Fworking class staple of the very rich
OL,10,Fculinary heritage of our capital city."
OL,12,FMr Zeichner said there are already
OL,13,FLondon foods with TSG status, such as
OL,14,FLondon cure smoked salmon.
OL,16,F"Products like these show how local
OL,17,Ftraditions can thrive and how we can
OL,18,Fcelebrate them for their authenticity
OL,19,Fand tradition, which has been
OL,20,Fdeveloped over a long, long time," he
OL,21,Fsaid.
