OL,3,C'Yes, Pie Minister': Government urged
OL,4,Cto give pie and mash protected status
OL,6,FThe minister went on to say: "The
OL,7,FGovernment is committed to celebrating
OL,8,Fthe UK's Geographical Indications and
OL,9,Fwill continue to promote them at home
OL,10,Fand abroad, working to ensure that the
OL,11,Fbenefits are felt across the country.
OL,13,F"Now while due process prevents me
OL,14,Ffrom commenting today on whether pie
OL,15,Fand mash would qualify for the TSG
OL,16,Fstatus, I would warmly welcome a
OL,17,Fformal application and I'm very
OL,18,Fpleased that my officials are working
OL,19,Fclosely with the proposal."
